{"tid":1509306,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[勇武x文宣] 請前線書法家入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-26T19:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T12:24:17.000Z","uid":240642,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6081419d65596a7e3a08e93991ca3f205355c6a3","tid":1509306,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:46:32.000Z","msg":"各位手足喺前線噴得字，都係想send a message 姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到近來大家開始轉英文想攞外媒注意，小弟有幾句拋書包精選，大家啱用就攞去：<br />\n<br />\n1. No taxation without representation<br />\n呢句係美國人都識，你識寫呢句野出嚟美國人J到甩褲都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至於點解啦喎：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">此口號概述了英國十三殖民地人民的不滿，這也是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國革命</span></strong>的主要原因之一。簡言之，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">殖民地</span></strong>中的許多人認為，因為他們在英國<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">議會中沒有被直接代表</span></strong>，所以任何它通過的關於殖民地稅收的法律，都是違憲的。[/size=3]</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2. We hold these truths to be self-evident, that all men are created equal<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國獨立宣言</span></strong>第二段，意思唔駛多講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係J出血之選<br />\n<br />\n3. You have nothing to lose but your chains! / We have nothing to lose but our chains!<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>共產黨宣言</strong></span>最後一句，以子之矛攻子之盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. That is the promise. And that is the unshakeable destiny.<br />\n彭定康<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">1997</span></strong>離開香港前最後果一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>[size=2](有時間絕對推介睇一次，睇撚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Governor%27s_Speech_at_Farewell_Ceremony_of_Hong_Kong_Handover_1997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2FGovernor%2527s_Speech_at_Farewell_Ceremony_of_Hong_Kong_Handover_1997&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQru8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=97ca4b1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Governor%27s_Speech_at_Farewell_Ceremony_of_Hong_Kong_Handover_1997</a>)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5. Tear down this Wall!<br />\n美國前總統列根喺柏林圍牆前對<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>東德同蘇聯共產黨</strong></span>講嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n霸氣之選<br />\n<br />\n6. Gorbachev or Hitler? Your choice, Xi.<br />\n呢句我自己作嘅。想做Gorbachev 將萬惡嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蘇聯解體</span></strong>，受全世界景仰，定做希特拉，走上<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>滅亡之路</strong></span>？自己揀啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望喺街見到你地發揮嘅小宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Sir this way！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b936d81cdfd7c436e290f73acc75a8bec3a9d623","tid":1509306,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQru8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=3e90f9b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQru8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=5790ac1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"h